				<title>Admin Post - Info - Open</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-103504/lowest-rated-pages#post-4716649</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2020 04:36:48 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Zyn</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1404533</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Please note that this discussion thread is not for announcing new SCP articles and soliciting readers; rather, authors should use the current SCP Announcements thread in the Announcements forum category to do so.</p> <p>Furthermore, assuming that downvotes are due to trolls is rather insulting to the readerbase, especially given that in this case the page was reposted twice (and as such in violation of <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/site-rules">Site Rules</a> twice). The deletion records are <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-13437096/deletions-67:beef-jerky-clams-grape-punch#post-4716187">here</a>.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
