					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This isn't a &quot;Wall of Shame&quot; list. It's purely meant as a tool to improve the quality of the site by flagging articles that fail to meet requirements. Nothing about it should be taken personal. I've been on this page too more than once. Chin up.</p> 
